36.37	Snatch_(film)	Snatch (film)	Snatch is a 2000 crime film written and directed by British filmmaker Guy Ritchie, featuring an ensemble cast. Set in the London criminal underworld, the film contains two intertwined plots: one dealing with the search for a stolen diamond, the other with a small-time boxing promoter named Turkish who finds himself under the thumb of a ruthless gangster known as Brick Top (Alan Ford).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/a7/Snatch_ver4.jpg/220px-Snatch_ver4.jpg
